    "c-f1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Art Direction \n\n A tongue-in-cheek parody of vintage studio titles, reimagined through the lens of a cannabis brand. Towering nugs, fireworks, and a classic silhouetted composition gave the piece a sense of overblown grandeur while keeping the joke clear.",
      "level": 4,
