            "duration": 0.45,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-f2": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Production Approach \n\n The cannabis nugs were built from CGI assets, then treated with an old-animation approach. We stacked illustrated cards, wrapped light around the forms, and layered the scene to create a sense of depth, movement, and theatrical scale.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
