        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.45,
            "delay": 0.1
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-f3": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Sound Design \n\n Using Dolby Atmos as a playground, we built a 3D soundscape that let the music move through the room instead of simply playing over the picture. The fireworks, swelled, exploded and wrapped the audience, ending with a perfectly timed *“woahhhhh”* from the front row.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "width": "100%",
